org.objectstyle.cayenne.access.util
Interface DependencySorter

All Known Subinterfaces:
EntitySorter
All Known Implementing Classes:
AshwoodEntitySorter, DefaultSorter, NullSorter
public interface DependencySorter

Interface that defines API to algorithms used for sorting Cayenne entities based on their dependencies.

Note that since 1.1 this interface is moved to EntitySorter and should be considered deprecated.

Author:
Andrei Adamchik
